                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8143" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1257</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2462 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东方甄选“硬核直播”出圈记</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">East selection &quot;Hardcore live&quot; in the ring</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">牟玲玲，高子叶，于子涵</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京新东方科技服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东方甄选；直播带货；农产品；情感营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Oriental selection; Live delivery; Agricultural products; Emotional marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本文以“东方甄选”作为案例研究对象，描述了作为教育机构的新东方到知识型直播带货农产品的”东方甄选”这个成功的转型过程，发现该直播间主要利用情感和知识来搭建农产品和消费者之间的桥梁，老师跨界成为主播进行双语直播带货，在带货的同时分享知识和自己的人生感悟，营造一种积极向上充满正能量的直播氛围。整篇文章通过展示东方甄选如何形成“农产品＋知识型”带货模式这一定位过程，来让学生理解市场定位的整体思路，同时带领学生把握4P、4I营销组合策略相关理论，在此框架下分析东方甄选的营销策略。在这个成功转型的背后还体现了俞敏洪、董宇辉身上的珍贵品质，因此通过提炼本案例中所蕴含思想价值和精神内涵来激发学生主体性，培养其坚韧不拔、永不言败的意志品质。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Taking &quot;Oriental Selection&quot; as the case study object, this paper describes the successful transformation process from New Oriental, an educational institution, to &quot;Oriental Selection&quot;, a knowledge-based live broadcast of agricultural products. It is found that this live broadcast mainly uses emotion and knowledge to build a bridge between agricultural products and consumers, and teachers become cross-boundary anchors for bilingual live broadcast of agricultural products. While bringing goods, we can share knowledge and our own perception of life to create a positive atmosphere full of positive energy. The whole article shows the process of how Oriental Selection forms &quot;agricultural products + knowledge-based&quot; delivery mode, so as to let students understand the overall idea of market positioning. Meanwhile, it leads students to grasp the relevant theories of 4P and 4I marketing mix strategy, and analyzes the marketing strategy of Oriental Selection under this framework. This successful transformation also reflects the precious qualities of Yu Minhong and Dong Yuhui. Therefore, by refining the ideological value and spiritual connotation contained in this case, students&#39; subjectivity is stimulated and their will quality of perseverance and never giving up is cultivated.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《网络营销》、《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销策略；东方甄选；直播带货；“农产品＋知识型”；市场定位</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-02</td>
                            </tr>
